        "TileImage": "$($repository 207f8711-832d-4458-89ea-ae6a9c5761af).Image",
        "Description": "Hello, there isn&apos;t much to say, yet there is a lot to say. Four of our clients have left us with bad taste in their mouths. We might not be able to bring them back but we sure want to do some damage control. These four targets have been up to no good, but frankly he have no good reason to take them out either. Some of these methods are our clients&apos; preferred methods. Use them, make them proud. \r\rThanks for you time. \r\rContract ID: 67193.",
